{"word":"ὀκνέω","slug":"ὀκνέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n72763\" key=\"o)kne/w\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"suff\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ὀκν-έω</orth>, <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"dialect\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ep.\">Ep.</a></gram> </gramGrp> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ὀκνείω</orth> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:5:255\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5.255</biblScope> </bibl> : <tns opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tns\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ impf.\">impf.</a></tns> <sense id=\"n72763.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ὤκνεον</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:20:155\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">20.155</biblScope> </bibl> </cit> : <tns opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tns\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ fut.\">fut.</a></tns> <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">-ήσω</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0010.tlg016.perseus-grc1:72\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Isoc.\">Isoc.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">6.72</biblScope> </bibl> </cit> : <tns opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tns\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ aor.\">aor.</a></tns> <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ὤκνησα</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0014.tlg018.perseus-grc1:103\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ D.\">D.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">18.103</biblScope></bibl></cit>, etc. : (<etym lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"etym\">ὄκνος</etym>) :—<tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">shrink from</tr_> doing, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">scruple, hesitate</tr_> to do a thing, c. <mood opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"mood\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ inf.\">inf.</a></mood>, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ὀκνείω ἵππων ἐπιβαινέμεν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:5:255\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5.255</biblScope> </bibl> </cit> ; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἀρχέμεναι πολέμοιο ὤκνεον</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:20:155\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">20.155</biblScope></bibl></cit>.—In <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"dialect\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Att.\">Att.</a></gram> </gramGrp> mostly with collat. sense of the feeling which causes the hesitation, and so, </sense> <sense n=\"1\" id=\"n72763.1\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> of shame or fear (in a moral sense), <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὀκνῶ προδότης καλεῖσθαι</foreign> I <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">shrink from</tr_> being called, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">fear</tr_> to be called, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0011.tlg006.perseus-grc1:93\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ S.\">S.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ph.\">Ph.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">93</biblScope></bibl>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0003.tlg001.perseus-grc1:5:61\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Th.\">Th.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5.61</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0540.tlg036:23\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a clas